      multiple independent RCAN registry nodes to interoperate as a coherent global namespace. It
      specifies how nodes identify themselves, partition the RRN namespace, synchronise records, and
      establish a verifiable trust chain rooted at <code class="text-cyan-400">rcan.dev</code>.
